      <abstract label="Abstract">The Larry McBryde Collection on the
        John McLaren McBryde Family contains materials concerning Dr. John McLaren McBryde and his
        family from 1859 through the 1920s. The collection includes photographs, newspaper
        clippings, correspondences, and publications. Additionally, copies of the correspondence
        between Dr. John McLaren McBryde and the University of Virginia pertain to an offer for its
        presidency.</abstract>
    </did>

